<section class="game-instructions">
  <h2>How to play</h2>
  <p>
    Objective: Click countries on the map and identify the country and its capital. The game is complete when the
    entire map is green (all countries and capitals have been guessed correctly).
  </p>

        <h3><i class="bi bi-joystick"></i> Map controls</h3>
        <p>The map uses Leaflet for interaction. Use these keyboard and mouse controls to navigate:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Pan map</strong>: <kbd>Arrow Keys</kbd> (Left/Right/Up/Down) or click and drag with the left mouse
                button.</li>
            <li><strong>Zoom in / out</strong>: Mouse wheel scroll (wheel up = zoom in, wheel down = zoom out), or press
                <kbd>+</kbd> or <kbd>-</kbd> on the keyboard.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Box zoom</strong>: Hold <kbd>Shift</kbd> and drag to draw a rectangle — the map will zoom to fit that
                box (Leaflet's box-zoom behavior).</li>
            <li><strong>Continent buttons</strong>: Click a continent button (if visible in the UI) to jump/zoom to that
                continent — this uses the map's continent zoom helper.</li>
            <li><strong>Zoom step keys</strong>: <kbd>=</kbd> usually behaves like <kbd>+</kbd> (useful on keyboards where +
                requires Shift).</li>
        </ul>

        <h3><i class="bi bi-palette"></i> Color legend</h3>
        <p>Result colors shown on the map indicate how well a country &amp; its capital were guessed:</p>
        <div class="color-legend">
            <div class="legend-item">
                <div class="legend-color" style="background:#28a745;"></div>
                <div class="legend-text">
                    <strong>Green</strong> — Both the country and its capital were guessed correctly.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="legend-item">
                <div class="legend-color" style="background:#ffc107;"></div>
                <div class="legend-text">
                    <strong>Yellow</strong> — Only the country was guessed correctly.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="legend-item">
                <div class="legend-color" style="background:#007bff;"></div>
                <div class="legend-text">
                    <strong>Blue</strong> — Only the capital was guessed correctly.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>